    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AccountService
    Service class responsible for account-related functionality such as: - Changing passwords for all user types (Applicant, Officer, Manager) - Registering new applicants into the system This class interacts with user databases and performs input validation during account modification or creation workflows.
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant user in the BTO system.
    ApplicantController
    Controller class for users with the Applicant role.
    ApplicantDB
    The ApplicantDB class manages the database of applicants.
    ApplicantView
    The ApplicantView class provides the user interface for applicants.
    Application<StatType>
    A generic class representing an application to a project.
    AuthController
    Controller that manages authentication-related actions, such as login, logout, password changes, and account creation.
    AuthService
    Service class responsible for authentication and login-related logic.
    BTOProject
    Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project with details such as unit types, prices, application period, project manager, officer slots, and assigned officers.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry made by a user regarding a BTO project, including the original question and optional reply details.
    EnquiryDB
    The EnquiryDB class manages the database of enquiries.
    EnquiryService
    Service class that handles all enquiry-related operations such as adding, viewing, editing, replying to, and deleting enquiries.
    FileLoader
    FileLoader is the utility class for loading data from CSV files into Java objects.
    FileSaver
    FileSaver is a class responsible for saving various types of data (e.g., applicants, officers, managers, projects, enquiries, and applications) into their respective CSV files.
    FilterCategory
    Enum representing the various filter categories that can be applied to search or display BTO projects in the system.
    FilterSettings
    Represents a set of filtering and sorting options used to narrow down BTO project listings.
    FilterSettings.SortBy
    Enum representing the available fields by which the results can be sorted.
    FilterUtil
    FilterUtil is a utility class for filtering BTOProject objects based on various criteria.
    FlatType
    Enum representing the type of flat offered in BTO projects.
    HDBManager
    Represents an HDB Manager in the BTO system.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer in the BTO system.
    IAccountService
    Interface defining account-related actions such as changing passwords and adding new applicant users.
    IAuthService
    Interface defining authentication services such as login and logout.
    IEnquiryService
    Interface defining enquiry-related operations including adding, editing, viewing, and replying to project enquiries.
    IFileLoader
    IFileLoader is an interface for loading application data from external sources (e.g., CSV files).
    IFileSaver
    IFileSaver is an interface for saving application data to external storage (e.g., CSV files).
    IOfficerApplicationService
    Interface for managing officer applications including creation, status update, and retrieval by project or user.
    IProjectApplicationService
    Interface for managing project applications by applicants.
    IProjectManagementService
    Interface for BTO project management.
    IReceiptPrintService
    Interface for generating booking receipts for successful applicants.
    IReportPrintService
    Interface for generating and filtering BTO project reports.
    ManagerController
    Controller class for HDB Managers.
    ManagerDB
    The ManagerDB class manages the database of HDB managers.
    ManagerView
    The ManagerView class provides the user interface for HDB managers.
    MaritalStatus
    Enum representing the marital status of a user.
    OfficerAppDB
    The OfficerAppDB class manages the database of officer applications.
    OfficerApplication
    Represents an application submitted by a user to become an officer for a BTO project.
    OfficerApplicationService
    Service class that handles officer application processes, including submission, filtering, retrieval, and status updates.
    OfficerAppStat
    Enum representing the status of an officer application.
    OfficerController
    Controller class for users with the HDB Officer role.
    OfficerDB
    The OfficerDB class manages the database of HDB officers.
    OfficerView
    The OfficerView class provides the user interface for HDB officers.
    ProjectAppDB
    The ProjectAppDB class manages the database of project applications.
    ProjectApplication
    Represents an application submitted by a user to apply for a BTO flat.
    ProjectApplicationService
    Service class that handles all functionalities related to project applications submitted by applicants, including application submission, status updates, withdrawals, bookings, and eligibility checks.
    ProjectAppStat
    Enum representing the status of a project application by an applicant.
    ProjectDB
    The ProjectDB class manages the database of BTO projects.
    ProjectManagementService
    Service class for managing BTO projects.
    ReceiptPrintService
    Service class responsible for generating booking receipts for applicants who have successfully secured a BTO flat.
    ReportPrintService
    Service class responsible for generating detailed reports on booked project applications.
    SortUtil
    SortUtil is a utility class for sorting BTOProject lists based on various attributes.
    User
    Represents a generic user in the system.
    UserController
    Abstract base class for all user controllers in the BTO system, including Applicant, Officer, and Manager controllers.
    UserView
    The UserView class provides a user interface for managing filter settings.
    ViewFormatter
    The ViewFormatter class provides utility methods for formatting output in the console.
